channel.title: Deltascape Cleaned
channel.description:
I have been working on deltascape server for a few days, I've made another one and packaged all the server together and added a lot of features, this source I created was just to clean a few things up.
I have cleaned this server for people who just want a normal deltascape source, as well, this can stop the leechers.
I don't think none of you need pictures for a basic wL server, but I can provide one, the server files looks a lot cleaner.
[img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/Thefiles.jpg[/img]
[b]Download link[/b] http://fileuploader.info/download.php?id=4D76C4651
[quote="Efilite"][quote author=i duh loot link=topic=370927.msg2802857#msg2802857 date=1243545561] looks like craaap, dont bather post this unless its worth downloading! [/quote] It's crap alright. Get used to it, all you young ones want is a server that is fully working has a lot of features and doesn't get attacked by bots.
Grow up and start learning some stuff, this server I done for my education purposes, I changed some little things around and learnt how the private server works.[/quote]
[b]Credits[/b] Delta_ Efilite wL
